21
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:09,000
The floor of the gymnasium suddenly caved in at an elementary school in Kakuba-cho, Koto Ward→

22
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:14,000
It is said that a teacher and several students fell into the collapsed hole.

23
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,000
(Momoko Nakazawa) What do you think?

24
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,000
(Hiroshi Shiratori) Let's change the cooling water. I'll get it.

25
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,000
yes.

26
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,000
Thank you for your hard work.

27
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:52,000
Um... did I do something?

28
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,000
Don't you remember anything?

29
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:06,000
I went to a bar and Momoko offered me tequila and when I refused, she laughed at me and said I was a piece of shit →

30
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:09,000
Feeling frustrated, I poured some tequila →

31
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:12,000
2 cups 3 cups…→

32
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:17,000
After about the 5th drink, my memory device completely broke down...

33
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
When I wake up, next to me...

34
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:29,000
If I do something wrong, I will pay for it with my life!

35
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,000
(sigh)

36
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Momoko-san?

37
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:37,000
(Norifumi Akase) Dispatch! Bud driving please.

38
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,000
yes!

39
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,000
chef. Car number 3.

40
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,000
yes. Car number 3?

41
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:54,000
(siren)

42
00:03:54,000 --> 00:04:00,000
♬〜

43
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:04,000
Elementary school in Kakuba-cho, Koto Ward...

44
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,000
yeah? Was there a cave-in accident?

45
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,000
That's right.

46
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:11,000
Is it related to a murder case?

47
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:14,000
Ah, I understand! Did a body come out of the hole?

48
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,000
