56
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
yeah? Momoko: How to say it.

57
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:49,000
🔊We will be the strength and hope for the disaster victims!

58
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:52,000
The first star is the first light that shines in the sky!

59
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,000
🔊This work is also typical of us!

60
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:57,000
(Suguro Hanji) He's the one who says nasty things.

61
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:01,000
