77
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,000
yes!

78
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,000
Oh my...

79
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:41,000
♬〜

80
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:45,000
Buds and Momoko are directing traffic around the school →

81
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,000
Securing flow lines for emergency vehicles. (Momoko/Tsubomi) Yes.

82
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,000
Miao-nee and Kuro-san set up a support booth.

83
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,000
(Suguro/Mio) Yes.

84
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:56,000
And about this third car →

85
00:06:56,000 --> 00:07:00,000
I also want to use it as a police box mode.

86
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:04,000
We take turns standing guard.

87
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:09,000
We would like to respond to inquiries and complaints from residents.

88
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,000
Everyone stand by the disaster victims →

89
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:16,000
We want to ensure safety around the site.

90
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:18,000
(All) Yes!

91
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Hat on!

92
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:27,000
♬〜

93
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:31,000
<This story is about seven unique detectives.>

94
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:37,000
This is a drama about a moving investigation headquarters vehicle, commonly known as Ichibanboshi, that solves cases.

95
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,000
Who fell into the hole?

96
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:50,000
(Firefighter Chief) Two students and a female teacher were in physical education class.

97
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:53,000
What's it like inside? It is not visible from the outside.

98
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,000
Thank you for your hard work.

99
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,000
🔊(Radio) The person in need of rescue cannot be seen due to dust.

100
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:04,000
🔊The risk of secondary collapse is extremely high around the cave-in area→

101
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:07,000
Temporarily abandon the entry of troops.

102
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:11,000
🔊Of the three people in need of rescue, one girl was found to have a chronic illness.

103
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:15,000
🔊The time limit from confirmation to the attending physician to rescue is 24 hours.

104
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
🔊It's already been 2 hours.

105
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:20,000
🔊Repeat. Of the three people who needed rescue, one girl had a chronic illness.

106
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:24,000
🔊The time limit for rescue is 24 hours. Two hours have already passed.

107
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,000
(Bio/Suguro) Seino...!

108
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
(Mio) Yay! Good...

109
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:38,000
Yes, yes, yes…. Thank you Kuro-san.

110
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:41,000
(Suguro) Mio-nee... (Mio) Ah, that too.

111
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,000
(Ryukichi Gunji) Ah~ah...

112
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:48,000
That's why I won't say anything. Because you don't listen to us.

113
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,000
(Kiyoshi Mitsui) That's true. Not at all.

114
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,000
(Mizue Bando) Yeah.

115
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,000
(wind chime sound)

116
00:08:54,000 --> 00:09:06,000
♬〜

117
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:10,000
Momoko-san: It happened yesterday...

118
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:14,000
Me in the room with you...

119
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,000
I'm at work.

120
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:49,000
♬〜

121
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:53,000
First in this town! Make this town great!

122
00:09:56,000 --> 00:10:00,000
I could not stand still after hearing the report of the cave-in accident →

123
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:04,000
I've come to take command of the rescue as the ward chief!

124
