131
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:34,000
Yes, we now have a sufficient amount of water, which was in short supply.

132
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,000
thank you.

133
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,000
What? this.

134
