524
00:36:27,066 --> 00:36:29,066
I haven't done anything like that...

525
00:36:32,066 --> 00:36:34,066
The villain's acting is bad.

526
00:36:36,066 --> 00:36:39,066
Ugh...noisy! Are you going to kick me?

527
00:36:41,066 --> 00:36:44,066
Everyone get out! This is my fortress!

528
00:36:44,066 --> 00:36:48,066
No, no, no, no. This car belongs to the police.

529
00:36:48,066 --> 00:36:54,066
Chief: You jumped into the police fortress on your own.

530
00:36:54,066 --> 00:36:57,066
Ichibanboshi Don't name it!

531
00:36:59,066 --> 00:37:01,066
yes. Huh?

