538
00:37:27,066 --> 00:37:31,066
Now then, I'm the head of the Ajima district. please.

539
00:37:32,066 --> 00:37:36,066
The rescue was successful.

540
00:37:36,066 --> 00:37:38,066
As the person in charge →

541
00:37:38,066 --> 00:37:43,066
